{"tid":305813,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"10日想去捷克, 奧地利, 德國 會否太趕","createTime":"2017-07-02T04:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T00:55:42.000Z","uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5baac01531c236acc684084fe9de5f4720328a2f","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"本身諗<br />\n布拉格 + CK (3日)<br />\nHallstatt + salazbg (住salazbg) (2日)<br />\n慕尼克 (2日)<br />\n其餘時間計落車程/ 飛機<br />\n1個人去 , 會唔會趕頭趕命<br />\n麻煩晒大家<br />\n<br />\n個人喜好係 古蹟同風景 CK既城堡 , Hallstatt 係最想睇 thx"},{"pid":"ba1e741bb9f69b1bf6dd3338813e002711fcb59b","tid":305813,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbf92a91680f2a35ecf49e73d882d38e14a3237","tid":305813,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"過來人答你會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你自己一個就無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e91671be42981bc6f2c10e012c41a8208b2f3","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點cut好..<br />\n<br />\n慕尼克 本身冇咩特別想去 但係飛機票平D 同埋salazbg 返去都係二個鐘內既事<br />\n<br />\n捷克好似又話名大於實 奧地利D 建築可能仲靚過佢..<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要去呢3個地方 , 有冇師兄推介下歐洲10日有咩好去 最好岩一個麻甩佬自由行 治安好些少既地方<br />\n<br />\nthx"},{"pid":"4c910e6de2e47b2dfa922d12ef869ac895ff0a68","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人答你會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你自己一個就無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前去日本經驗 就算酒店係車站隔離 都搵路搵左半個鐘<br />\n所以預太蚊水既話 一陣走左班車/ 有咩突發事 就會行程亂晒.. 所以最好預鬆D.."},{"pid":"f74c6e422244a891c0f7a801851de02b94552f74","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&h=591951fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩先手痕search 機票 應該呢張 5千內唔知連左稅未 還可以 唔駛廿幾個鐘"},{"pid":"d61243209987fcae3d697a22bcac41bbf3dba003","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&h=591951fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩先手痕search 機票 應該呢張 5千內唔知連左稅未 還可以 唔駛廿幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&d=3kuNeJD51JJbiD%2FxdPUtNJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0da3d5aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr</a>"},{"pid":"37c7acb780d65e83cd0eff8249560b7809bb4b02","tid":305813,"uid":86352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"Ck好垃圾<br />\n半日都嫌多<br />\n個城堡啲石紋畫上去嘅<br />\n又冇心保養<br />\n啲樓梯就嚟甩出嚟咁又多蜘蛛網<br />\n遠睇還好<br />\n近睇不了<br />\n<br />\n捷克布拉格玩兩日感受一下氣氛就好<br />\n去太耐就會發覺好多嘢都係虛有其表<br />\n冇乜好食嘅嘢不單止<br />\n仲要啲鋪頭有啲racist<br />\n黃種人白人買嘢唔同價<br />\n成日比人西口西面<br />\n又借啲宜唔找錢咁樣<br />\n嗰次去食完餐飯圍番條數百幾蚊港紙都諗住唔找<br />\n另外就係蝗蟲同泡菜仲多過白人<br />\n但布拉格真係幾靚嘅"},{"pid":"0a01c4cb6919785f2db120783e1b6482a4fed46c","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"上網睇班人都話捷克好似歐洲版既中國...<br />\nck 果D 都係得中國人香港人去多<br />\n去布拉格留二日 直接去salazbg 會唔會冇咁趕"},{"pid":"654e877f79d9b98cf1948218a34c15d8d349a689","tid":305813,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&h=591951fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩先手痕search 機票 應該呢張 5千內唔知連左稅未 還可以 唔駛廿幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&d=3kuNeJD51JJbiD%2FxdPUtNJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0da3d5aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr</a></blockquote><br />\n即係你未買機票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f12b694c95f63a58056bd5efc3385d486232518","tid":305813,"uid":59203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"而家係維也納等車去斯洛伐克，同你講一定會好趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n德國Munich可以少啲"},{"pid":"79ac4e57ac0a64f57bdeb78a90cf088fa540fbaa","tid":305813,"uid":71230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"Munich商業區冇咩地方好玩，多數都係去新天鵝堡，prague+ck兩日夠"},{"pid":"ed430d71b3ec83cde059dec0ceba641f6670140c","tid":305813,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"我14日去德國荷蘭都覺得遺憾太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476a2c6d037526bdc33abb9e18d7b56762bedb49","tid":305813,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"去得 Salzburg就要留一日去國王湖"},{"pid":"d5d2c8aa24c24a6ca89f11c96fc1c0e0d653324b","tid":305813,"uid":49280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"緊係趕頭趕命<br />\n你諗下一個paypal一次拎80 steam game錢<br />\n你拎撚左五萬,點會唔趕,<br />\n你又要趕住告steam呢"},{"pid":"49e21cc1cc60ba0bb2ab31c04fd4bbf88d9b69e5","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&h=591951fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩先手痕search 機票 應該呢張 5千內唔知連左稅未 還可以 唔駛廿幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FPUZmr&d=3kuNeJD51JJbiD%2FxdPUtNJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0da3d5aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/PUZmr</a></blockquote><br />\n即係你未買機票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未買 度緊行程"},{"pid":"8deaf6beef9e3b4853663f5b0e4a84461111ff77","tid":305813,"uid":63177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"德國漢莎有時特價連稅都係4千直飛慕尼黑 ，又可以選擇柏林入慕尼黑走 你可以留意下。無轉機咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我去年10月去。我買左3千尾"},{"pid":"827e17148c0d1aecaea87e3096cdc127b5b03ffc","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國漢莎有時特價連稅都係4千直飛慕尼黑 ，又可以選擇柏林入慕尼黑走 你可以留意下。無轉機咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我去年10月去。我買左3千尾</blockquote><br />\n多謝晒 有直航緊係最好"},{"pid":"a6504ae59d0ac1457b7588783beead977d745ba9","tid":305813,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"Hallstatt一日絕對唔夠 兩日先夠<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/205755_765bfe71981c903284391f3d030668ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F205755_765bfe71981c903284391f3d030668ee.jpg&h=b009d338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上上星期去完冰洞 之後行一陣上山就有呢個風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非常建議去"},{"pid":"1d47da97af7eefc6c1304e9b1d99400c3074c8ce","tid":305813,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"之前去左兩日prague+1日ck 後來先發現brno都幾靚<br />\n班捷克人真心幾無禮貌，但個城市又真係靚啵<br />\n同埋洗費抵好多<br />\n不過你去十日既話 不如捷克入 波蘭走<br />\n波蘭都好多野玩"},{"pid":"5b8bdf916d11ba81f5dee47f6c85ae106c77912b","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"thanks 但周圍