國用Frankfurt做中心點玩周邊都用左六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSkip 捷克會好d？</blockquote><br />\n三個國家有無好想睇既野先？<br />\n我去德國果次針對Heidelberg同koln,連埋Christmas Market所以六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈斯塔特 應該必去 睇網上吹到全世界最靓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/041407_b9e8c022cb6b6ec3b970f87a11ac04fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F041407_b9e8c022cb6b6ec3b970f87a11ac04fe.jpg&h=f7eb9232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/041408_b3ee37b871291a73c4fd5d196c868c86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F041408_b3ee37b871291a73c4fd5d196c868c86.jpg&h=a465d354&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/041408_dc708868fd40eef6e09224a6d65206e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F041408_dc708868fd40eef6e09224a6d65206e3.jpg&h=f867753e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f076b7c68444ad466737262c2c38bc3c9d2aa75","tid":305813,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔會 布拉格一日行得哂<br />\nsalzburg其實冇咩特別 行陣就可以搭車去hallstatt 建議你住Bad Goisern 係正中間 果到有間airbnb唔錯 訓醒再去hallstatt<br />\n四月先去完瑞士-奧地利-捷克<br />\n後悔係布拉格stay 2日 d垃圾遊記話兩三日 懷疑寫果d都傷殘 都可能係我已經去過太多地方冇咩感覺"},{"pid":"9300e174da2241245330c651c13a80ba973fb1e2","tid":305813,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會 布拉格一日行得哂<br />\nsalzburg其實冇咩特別 行陣就可以搭車去hallstatt 建議你住Bad Goisern 係正中間 果到有間airbnb唔錯 訓醒再去hallstatt<br />\n四月先去完瑞士-奧地利-捷克<br />\n後悔係布拉格stay 2日 d垃圾遊記話兩三日 懷疑寫果d都傷殘 都可能係我已經去過太多地方冇咩感覺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor