\n<br />\n有人7日玩晒仲好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到門口打卡就收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHallstatt 去到又唔去salt mine, Gosausee , 5 finger ice cave , 去check point 影相就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932fa90db3cdbad1a75b332b83a1867fad1758ec","tid":305813,"uid":72948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個月<br />\n布拉格-&gt;CK-&gt; Hallstatt-&gt;Salzburg-&gt;國王湖-&gt; M&uuml;nich<br />\n加埋用左唔夠7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n走馬看花好好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b242bf93fef7896835daf912a3c89c2aa9a76b7d","tid":305813,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Salzburg 唔識玩咪悶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係識　去古城，一日玩得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，unterburg? Hellburn? St Wolfgang ?呢度都悶既話全歐洲80%悶<br />\nPrague 1 日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 城堡區，舊城區+猶太區，高堡區<br />\n睇怕都係去門口打卡就完工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人7日玩晒仲好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到門口打卡就收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHallstatt 去到又唔去salt mine, Gosausee , 5 finger ice cave , 去check point 影相就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsalzburg +附近小鎮 我行左4-5日都唔悶<br />\n特別係d 鬼佬節日聖誕節新年去既話會有市集"},{"pid":"65408e62f59c47fea4b8e794b1ea9861ff290f3b","tid":305813,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img 